.LP
This function is used when implementing an alternative distribution carrier using processes as distribution controllers\&. \fIDHandle\fR\& is retrived via the callback \fB\fIf_handshake_complete\fR\&\fR\&\&. More information can be found in the documentation of \fBERTS User\&'s Guide ➜ How to implement an Alternative Carrier for the Erlang Distribution ➜ Distribution Module\fR\&\&.
