Key = Val = term()
.br
.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
Returns the value \fIVal\fR\& associated with \fIKey\fR\& and deletes it from the process dictionary\&. Returns \fIundefined\fR\& if no value is associated with \fIKey\fR\&\&. Example:
.LP
