.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
Returns a binary corresponding to the text representation of \fIFloat\fR\& using fixed decimal point formatting\&. \fIOptions\fR\& behaves in the same way as \fB\fIfloat_to_list/2\fR\&\fR\&\&. Examples:
.LP
