.fi
.RE
.LP
.nf

.B
halt(Status) -> no_return()
.br
.fi
.br
.RS
.LP
Types:

.RS 3
Status = integer() >= 0 | abort | string()
.br
.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
The same as \fB\fIhalt(Status, [])\fR\&\fR\&\&. Example:
.LP
.nf

> halt(17)\&.
os_prompt% echo $?
