.B
list_to_atom(String) -> atom()
.br
.fi
.br
.RS
.LP
Types:

.RS 3
String = string()
.br
.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
Returns the atom whose text representation is \fIString\fR\&\&.
.LP
As from Erlang/OTP 20, \fIString\fR\& may contain any Unicode character\&. Earlier versions allowed only ISO-latin-1 characters as the implementation did not allow Unicode characters above 255\&. For more information on Unicode support in atoms, see \fBnote on UTF-8 encoded atoms\fR\& in section "External Term Format" in the User\&'s Guide\&.
.LP
Example:
.LP
.nf

> list_to_atom("Erlang")\&.
'Erlang'
.fi
.RE
.LP
.nf

