.br
.fi
.br
.RS
.LP
Types:

.RS 3
IoList = iolist()
.br
.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
Returns a binary that is made from the integers and binaries in \fIIoList\fR\&, for example:
.LP
.nf

> Bin1 = <<1,2,3>>\&.
<<1,2,3>>
> Bin2 = <<4,5>>\&.
<<4,5>>
> Bin3 = <<6>>\&.
<<6>>
> list_to_binary([Bin1,1,[2,3,Bin2],4|Bin3])\&.
<<1,2,3,1,2,3,4,5,4,6>>
.fi
