.RS 2
.TP 2
*
\fIregistered_name\fR\& (if the port has a registered name)
.LP
.TP 2
*
\fIid\fR\&
.LP
.TP 2
*
\fIconnected\fR\&
.LP
.TP 2
*
\fIlinks\fR\&
.LP
.TP 2
*
\fIname\fR\&
.LP
.TP 2
*
\fIinput\fR\&
.LP
.TP 2
*
\fIoutput\fR\&
.LP
.RE

.LP
For more information about the different \fIItem\fR\&s, see \fB\fIport_info/2\fR\&\fR\&\&.
.LP
Failure: \fIbadarg\fR\& if \fIPort\fR\& is not a local port identifier, or an atom\&.
