.RS
.LP
Removes old code for \fIModule\fR\&\&. Before this BIF is used, \fB\fIcheck_process_code/2\fR\&\fR\&is to be called to check that no processes execute old code in the module\&.
.LP

.RS -4
.B
Warning:
.RE
This BIF is intended for the code server (see \fB\fIcode(3)\fR\&\fR\&) and is not to be used elsewhere\&.

.LP

.RS -4
.B
Note:
.RE
