.LP
Sets the default maximum heap size settings for processes\&. The size is specified in words\&. The new \fImax_heap_size\fR\& effects only processes spawned efter the change has been made\&. \fImax_heap_size\fR\& can be set for individual processes using \fB\fIspawn_opt/2,3,4\fR\&\fR\& or \fB\fIprocess_flag/2\fR\&\fR\&\&.
